# Linear search returns index or -1.
*find(xs as Vec of i64, target as i64) returns i64
    i is 0
    while i < xs.length
        if xs.get(i) equals target
            return i
        i is i + 1
    -1

*main
    xs is vec()
    xs.push(10)
    xs.push(20)
    xs.push(30)
    log find(xs, 20)
    log find(xs, 99)
